title: Lakeshore East! Luxury Building! Near Streeterville!
posting_body: Call Apartment Guys and ask for reference #2192764.
The lovely modern hirise is tucked away in the serene Lakeshore East area just blocks from the lakefront and the exciting streeterville area!
The units have floor to ceiling windows, updated appliances including a dishwasher and microwave as well a washer and dryer conveniently located in the building.
The building amenities include garage parking, an outdoor pool, doorstaff, a dog run, bike storage, game and billiards room, and a spa and sauna.
Prices are subject to change.***Photos may be of a similar unit.or examples****For faster response best to call or text 773-549-3474 with reference #2192764
